  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "EHS Executive - Documentation (Loyang/MFG Co)",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Maintains and evaluates the effectiveness of the organization’s EHS Management System (EHSMS) by managing EHS administrative processes ie procedure/manuals.</p></li><li><p>Support EHS maintenance based on ISO9001(QMA), ISO 45001 and ISO 14001(EMS), RBA and other customer requirements.</p></li><li><p>Participate/coordinate in and follow up EHS related audits, e.g. Safety Audit on Managing Hazardous Substances, CERT Audit, audit by customers, agency survey, license management etc.</p></li><li><p>Support internal and external EHS audit, follow-up corrective measures with relevant stakeholders.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and conduct EHS related trainings/briefings/toolbox meetings and conduct EHS orientations for newly hired staff.</p></li><li><p>Using a range of WSH tools and resources to implement WSH programs and drive compliance.</p></li><li><p>Analytical and values teamwork and collaboration to solve problems.</p></li><li><p>Communicate the importance of WSH program compliance to team members of other departments.</p></li><li><p>Support and conduct workplace risk assessment and environmental impact and related training.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in WSHO related disciplines with 2 years of working experience in a manufacturing environment</p></li><li><p>Good team player, independent, pro-active and positive attitude in a fast-paced work environment</p></li><li><p>Excellent analytical, interpersonal, communication and reporting writing skills</p></li><li><p>Good knowledge of government authorities’ requirements</p></li><li><p>Ability to interpret Risk Assessment Registers requirements</p></li><li><p>Computer literate</p></li></ul><p><strong>5 days work week</strong></p><p><strong>Electronics Engineering</strong></p><p><strong>Loyang Area</strong><br /></p><p>Interested Applicants, kindly email your detailed resume to <a href=\"mailto:hr@tempserv.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>hr@tempserv.com.sg</strong></a></p><p><strong>Tempserv Pte Ltd</strong></p><p>License No: 06C3745</p><p><strong>Attention: Audris Teo / EA Personnel No: R1102063</strong></p>",
